The '''Ghoul''', also known as the '''GHOUL''', is an [[undead]] enemy in ''[[Final Fantasy]]''. Its attacks may cause [[Paralysis (Final Fantasy status)|Paralysis]], and it is infamous for its tendency to attack in large, chain-paralyzing packs alongside its [[Ghast (Final Fantasy)|Ghast]] cousin, prematurely ending many a [[Warriors of Light|Warrior of Light]]'s journey.

