== Battle ==
Ghouls are infamous for being the first enemy players encounter capable of inflicting [[Paralysis]] with their standard attack, and have a tendency to [[Paralysis|paralyze]] the party's frontliners. It is a good idea to save casts of [[Fire (ability)|Fire]] on the party's [[Black Mage (Final Fantasy)|Black Mage]] and to not be afraid to bust out [[Dia (ability)|Dia]] on the [[White Mage (Final Fantasy)|White Mage]].

